snippet.title: Blood Rage: Digital Edition - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
The digital adaptation of the legendary Viking board game designed by Eric M. Lang will be launched on Steam in 2020! 

Ragnarök has come, and it’s the end of the world. It’s the Vikings’ last
chance to go down in a blaze of glory and secure their place in Valhalla at Odin’s side! Fight like a Viking for honor and glory! 

Asmodee Digital's channels can be found below:

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/AsmodeeDigital
Twitter: https://twitter.com/AsmodeeDigital
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/asmodeedigital
